    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "この間放送された釣り番組、かなり評判がいいそうだ\nプロデューサーが雫にまた出てほしいと言っていたぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard the fishing program that aired the other day was well received.\nThe producer mentioned they’d like to have you on again‚ Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1652040482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "私も釣り、好きだから……\n好きなことがお仕事に繋がるのは、嬉しい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I like fishing too‚ so…\nI'm happy that my hobby is connected to work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8042678197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "趣味は釣りって、ライブのフリートークでも\nたまに話題に出してるよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "During the free talk time at lives‚ you sometimes mention that\nyour hobby is fishing‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9549603701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "最近もらったファンレターに……\n私がきっかけで釣りを始めたって書いてあった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In a fan letter I received recently…\nit said that a fan started fishing because of me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8878266912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "私がきっかけって言われるの……凄く嬉しかった……\nこういう時、アイドルになって良かったって思う……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It made me really happy to hear that it was because of me…\nIt's times like these that I feel glad to be an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5022352854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "もっと沢山の人に、釣りの楽しさを伝えたい……\nだから、釣りのお仕事……どんどん入れてほしい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to share the joy of fishing with more people…\nSo please… give me more fishing-related jobs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "釣りの親善大使か……\nそういうのもアイドルらしいかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A fishing ambassador? hmm…\nThat sounds like something an idol would do.",
        "id": ""
      },
